item.title: covid interesting founding
item.description: Abstract Nowadays, we are facing a difficult time, because of COVID19. As a people who live in toronto, is really care about the covid19 cases in toronto. For covid 19, there maybe some interesting foundings based from statistical ways, this blog is to find the interesting part of age and source of infection of who was infected by COVID19 in toronto. Introduction I selected the COVID19 toronto cases dataset to analyze.
